to speak first.

04:31.468 --> 04:33.470
Don't be shy.

04:36.112 --> 04:38.335
- Um, I often find

04:38.435 --> 04:40.537
that it helps
to have a talisman

04:40.637 --> 04:42.980
to encourage
the flow of conversation.

04:43.080 --> 04:45.642
So, um, does anyone have,
like, a conch?

04:47.764 --> 04:49.506
Okay, yeah.

04:49.606 --> 04:50.827
