This will work.

04:50.927 --> 04:54.271
Um, personally,

04:54.371 --> 04:56.874
I have been doing
a lot of soul-searching

04:56.974 --> 04:59.116
about whether or not
my own biases

04:59.216 --> 05:01.038
have contributed
to the problems

05:01.138 --> 05:03.440
