all: Oh!

25:46.231 --> 25:47.653
- Hey, hey, hey, hey.

25:47.753 --> 25:49.535
When Max's company goes public
and I got stock options,

25:49.635 --> 25:51.737
you'll all be calling me
Slumdog Tobillionaire.

