37:24.214 --> 37:25.756
and I noticed you were talking

37:25.856 --> 37:27.598
about white people
who worked at Sprqpoint.

37:27.698 --> 37:28.839
- Yeah.

37:28.939 --> 37:31.522
- And, um,
I just want to apologize

37:31.622 --> 37:33.524
for any undo harm
I might've caused

37:33.624 --> 37:35.446
as a beneficiary of a society

37:35.546 --> 37:37.207
