37:37.307 --> 37:40.531
- Leif, Leif, Leif, Leif,
dude, we're good, we're good,

37:40.631 --> 37:44.415
but, honestly, as your bro...

37:44.515 --> 37:45.976
[sighs]
You gotta dial it back

37:46.076 --> 37:47.498
on all the virtue signaling
stuff, man.

37:47.598 --> 37:49.059
You're doing too much.

37:49.159 --> 37:50.341
You know?

37:50.441 --> 37:53.023
- Okay, yeah.
Um...

37:53.123 --> 37:54.705
Wow, you know,
and even in discussing

37:54.805 --> 37:56.867
my own internal biases,
we're creating a dialogue.

37:56.967 --> 37:58.509
- Seriously, stop it.

37:58.609 --> 37:59.470
- Mm-hmm.
I can hear it.

37:59.570 --> 38:01.192
- Yeah.

38:01.292 --> 38:02.753
- Do you wanna get a beer?
- Yes!

38:02.853 --> 38:04.115
- Okay, great.
- Yes.

38:04.215 --> 38:05.636
- I found a guy who sells it
out of a vintage stagecoach.

38:05.736 --> 38:07.278
- And we're back.

38:07.378 --> 38:09.200
- I'm glad you like beer,
'cause I...

38:09.300 --> 38:11.642
- ♪ We don't have to go out ♪

38:11.742 --> 38:13.284
♪ ♪

