38:22.673 --> 38:24.655
The rest is just
a series of apologies.

38:24.755 --> 38:26.217
- Wow, that press release
went out fast.

38:26.317 --> 38:27.458
Whatever you said to them,

38:27.558 --> 38:29.420
it must've rocked them
to the core.

38:29.520 --> 38:32.543
- I mean, I hit them
with a few body shots.

38:32.643 --> 38:34.305
- Yeah, you did,

38:34.405 --> 38:36.507
like a drunk white girl
in Daytona.

38:36.607 --> 38:38.109
♪ ♪

38:38.209 --> 38:39.590
You don't know my past.

38:39.690 --> 38:41.072
- Toast, everybody, toast.
I wanna make a toast!

38:41.172 --> 38:42.753
Max, get out the kitchen!

38:42.853 --> 38:44.635
- Sorry, sorry, I was just
putting together some TV stands

38:44.735 --> 38:46.437
and a lazy Susan back there.

38:46.537 --> 38:48.079
Guess who's not lazy.
